        </div>

        <!-- WJ125 — "Print / Save as PDF" REMOVED from the public journey: the
             figured document no longer renders here, so there is nothing to
             print. The full PDF is downloaded from /proposition/<token> (sent by
             the sales rep). The old "Instant estimate…" line is removed too:
