               never a confirmed booking, no calendar dependency, no online
               payment/deposit (the online-deposit question stays a WG13
               founder decision, not built here). A human confirms the real
               slot after contact. WJ105 — this SAME control also serves as the
               "preferred callback window" when phone_ok is chosen (linked by
               the SLA sentence above, never a duplicate control). -->
          <fieldset class="mt-1">
            <legend id="mt-visit-legend" class="text-sm text-lune-soft">Preferred technical visit slot (optional)</legend>
            <p id="mt-visit-help" class="mt-1 text-xs text-lune-faint">A preference, not a booking — we confirm the exact slot with you.</p>
